{"tid":1718362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[人工多過你署長369] 彭博：投資銀行員工中環放工被捕　花旗籲員工遠離衝突","createTime":"2019-11-13T23:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T02:39:34.000Z","uid":54373,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2c7b43c821a570f966ca54a120bad0e0c02999bd","tid":1718362,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T23:34:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">毅進仔，其實你踏入中環一刻，你已經輸x咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n彭博報道，花旗集團一名投資銀行員工昨日中環行人路上被警方拘捕，有關片段昨日在社交媒體廣傳媒。根據片段，一名男子在中環被警員拘捕，他被捕前以英文稱其辦公室僅在500米外，被警員辱罵，「我同你我毅進（仔），我乜都冇得輸，我拉鳩你。」<br />\n<br />\n彭博報道指出，事件發生之後，花旗集團向在港員工警告，避免參與非法集會，呼籲員工盡量留在家中，確保家庭安全。彭博引述一名不願透露身份的知情人士指，花旗在電話會議內中要求員工避開警方及示威者之間的衝突。<br />\n<br />\n花旗發言人 James Griffiths 指出，知道有關事件，並正展開進一步調查，調查還在進行所以不便進一步發表評論，希望所有員工守法。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，與花旗相關的一名投資銀行員工的片段，在社交媒體上廣泛流傳，片段顯示一名上班裝束的男士，在中環行人路上被三名警員包圍，據網上流傳片段，該名男子在中環置地廣場外行人路被警員包圍時稱，他以英文表示其辦公室僅在500米外，稱自己無挑釁警員，認為警員「非法拘捕」。警員回應指，「我同你我毅進（仔），我乜都冇得輸，我拉鳩你。咪咁自大，我同你講。讀乜嘢書呀，柒頭。」在被捕過程，男子一度抓住和揮舞警棍，最後被強壓在力。"},{"pid":"d67f71f1bd7084e1b6ea66b27b10bf5f1321cdfe","tid":1718362,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:38:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cbed6e3a3cdb7931ef965122b28ace13028ba0e","tid":1718362,"uid":129739,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:39:56.000Z","msg":"citi都on99，係佢員工唔守法定偽進仔唔守法呀？"},{"pid":"5ea03b769fadae4deaf49ea6682dc906a508af2f","tid":1718362,"uid":74672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:41:12.000Z","msg":"被警員辱罵，「我同你<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我毅進</strong></span>（仔），我乜都冇得輸，我拉鳩你。」<br />\n<br />\n辱罵緊自己？"},{"pid":"14d80568766cc1711d739ebb9b456691ba151a0e","tid":1718362,"uid":72863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:44:05.000Z","msg":"推上國際啦！"},{"pid":"182bef3145fc0aca5ff95c53b8239f43f9ecfefe","tid":1718362,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:47:52.000Z","msg":"篇野你寫架，咁多錯別字"},{"pid":"924664e5b52de754df3722a19f7f97324bb675e1","tid":1718362,"uid":265839,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:47:56.000Z","msg":"如果send 晒比國際banker，話香港好危險，中共隨時強行對ibank &quot;執法&quot;，唔知會點呢"},{"pid":"c86eb83a8ac14554bd555e941bed4db1408356a7","tid":1718362,"uid":75959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5ea03b769fadae4deaf49ea6682dc906a508af2f","tid":1718362,"uid":74672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:41:12.000Z","msg":"被警員辱罵，「我同你<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我毅進</strong></span>（仔），我乜都冇得輸，我拉鳩你。」<br />\n<br />\n辱罵緊自己？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:49:10.000Z","msg":"自卑變自大"},{"pid":"a8653dafcfd5eb443e4564c0e492363b2d62a323","tid":1718362,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T00:49:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756a453114567126fe9ec364bc88b48b102d97b7","tid":1718362,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40dcc0963435b1488834d8927ad2cb030dbc3997","tid":1718362,"uid":84013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:04:21.000Z","msg":"有冇片?"},{"pid":"3202b2ca21b81559b339dcd7c4a5c7688dba64c6","tid":1718362,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:06:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal